ides.api.plugin.model
Interface ParentModel

All Superinterfaces:
Annotable, DESModel, DESModelPublisher
public interface ParentModel
extends DESModel

Interface for DESModels which, in turn, contain other DESModels as child models. An example would be a hierarchical system.

Author:
Lenko Grigorov
